title: Music Guru
body: Enjoy this music trivia game! This project gives you an opporutnity to listen to short clips of music and guess which song is correct from a list of options. You will get immediate feedback on your answer and transtion through the game easily. I contributed heavily to the design and CSS components of this site. I worked on the functionality as well.
